# social_svg
Sets of svg (base64) for social share

Google plus :
<pre ```html>
<img style="border-radius: 50%;" class="no-showy" width="0" height="0" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
</pre>

Twitter :
<pre ```html>
<img style="border-radius: 50%;" class="showy" width="0" height="0" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
</pre>

Facebook
<pre ```html>
<img style="border-radius: 50%;" class="showy" width="0" height="0" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
</pre>
